quran[9{c,v,t}:
18,75,"uss ne kaha"" mein ne tum se kaha nah tha ke tum mere sath sabr nahi kar satke? """
18,76,"moose ne kaha"" is ke baad agar mein aap se kuch pouchon to aap mujhe sath nah rakhen lijiye, ab to meri taraf se aap ko izr mil gaya """
18,77,"phir woh agay chalay yahan taq ke aik bastii mein puhanche aur wahan ke logon se khana manga magar unhon ne un dono ki ziyafat se inkaar kar diya wahan unhon ne aik deewar dekhi jo gira chahti thi uss shakhs ne is deewar ko phir qaim kar diya moose ne kaha"" agar aap chahtay to is kaam ki aُjrt le satke thay """
18,78,"uss ne kaha"" bas mera tumhara sath khatam howa ab mein tumhe un baton ki haqeeqat batata hon jin par tum sabr nah kar sakay"
18,79,"uss kashti ka maamla yeh hai ke woh chand ghareeb admion ki thi jo darya mein mehnat mazdoori karte thay mein ne chaha ke usay aib daar kar dun, kyunkay agay aik aisay badshah ka ilaqa tha jo har kashti ko zabardasti chean laita tha"
18,80,"raha woh larka, to is ke walidain momin thay, hamein andesha howa ke yeh larka apni sar kashi aur kufar se un ko tang kere ga"
18,81,is liye hum ne chaha ke un ka rab is ke badlay un ko aisi aulaad day jo ikhlaq mein bhi is se behtar ho aur jis se sila rehmi bhi ziyada mutawaqqa ho
18,82,"aur is deewar ka maamla yeh hai ke yeh do yateem larkoon ki hai jo is shehar mein rehtay hain is deewar ke neechay inn bchchon ke liye aik khazana madfoon hai aur un ka baap aik naik aadmi tha is liye tumahray rab ne chaha ke yeh dono bachay baaligh hon aur apna khazana nikaal len yeh tumahray rab ki rehmat ki bana parkia gaya hai, mein ne kuch apne ikhtiyar se nahi kar diya hai yeh hai haqeeqat unn baton ki jin par tum sabr nah kar sakay """
18,83,"aur ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, yeh log tum se zwalqrnin ke baray mein puchhte hain un se kaho, mein is ka kuch haal tum ko sunataa hon"
